==English==
===Etymology===
From {{Gr.}} ''[[γλυκός]]'' (glykos) sweet, + [[-ose]], suffix used in forming the names of sugars

===Noun===
'''glucose''' (''[[uncountable]]'')
{{wikipedia}}
